Package: bikerentaldata
Title: Build Daily Capital Bikeshare Analysis Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    c(
      person(
        given = "Christopher",
        family = "Odoom",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "odoomchristopher22@gmail.com"
      )
    )
Description: Discovers and downloads official Capital Bikeshare annual and
    monthly trip archives, summarizes station locations, aggregates trips into
    daily registered and casual rental counts, combines them with daily
    weather observations, adds calendar variables, and validates the resulting
    analysis data. The package contains processing code but does not
    redistribute the full third-party dataset.
